{"article_id":"4Tp7S3xqxdbxIfaz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"At least 10 people are dead","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after a 17-year-old student allegedly opened fire at Santa Fe High School in Texas this morning ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"sending students fleeing for their lives ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the governor said .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Interested in Santa Fe School Shooting ?","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Add Santa Fe School Shooting as an interest","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Santa Fe School Shooting news , video , and analysis from .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Add Interest","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Ten others were wounded ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"including a police officer","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"who is in critical condition ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"officials said .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"A teacher is among the dead ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"according to law enforcement officials .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Gov . Greg Abbott called the shooting `` one of the most heinous attacks","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that we 've ever seen in the history of Texas schools . ''","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The suspect , 17-year-old Dimitrios Pagourtzis , is in custody","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"and has been charged with capital murder ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"officials said .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The suspect allegedly wrote in journals","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"that he wanted to carry out the shooting","depth":15},{"id":21,"text":"and then commit suicide ,","depth":15},{"id":22,"text":"but he gave himself up to authorities ,","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"according to Abbott .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"At the Santa Fe Police Department , Pagourtzis gave a statement","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"admitting to shooting multiple people inside the school with the intent","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"of killing people ,","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"according to an probable cause affidavit .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Pagourtzis also allegedly stated during the interview","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"that he did not shoot students","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"he liked","depth":16},{"id":31,"text":"`` so he could have his story told , ''","depth":15},{"id":32,"text":"the affidavit states .","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"There were no warning signs","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and the suspect does n't have a criminal history ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"officials said .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"A second individual , a person of interest , has been detained ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"officials said .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Two weapons were used in the massacre","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"-- a shotgun and a .38 revolver --","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"both of which appear to be legally owned by the suspect 's father ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"the governor said .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` I have no information","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"if the father was aware","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"the son had taken these weapons from the father , ''","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Abbott added .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Explosive devices were also found at the school ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and devices","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"including a Molotov cocktail","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"were found in a car and a home ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"authorities said .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Freshman Peter Matuza was in art class this morning","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"when he heard two explosions","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and ducked under a table ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The gunman shot Peter ' s friend with a shotgun","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"before turning","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and opening fire with a revolver ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Peter told .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Students were running","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"and screaming","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"and one student flipped a table over for cover ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Peter said .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Peter said","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"he made eye contact with the suspect ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"noting ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"`` he had a face of rage . ''","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"The gunman then \" walked through a closet","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"that went straight to the adjacent art room","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"and began opening fire in there , as well , \"","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Peter said .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Bryton Sumbles , a former football player for the school , told","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that he reported Pagourtzis to teachers in the past","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"because he thought","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"it was odd","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"that he would wear trench coats in 97-degree weather ,","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"and he thought","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"it would be easy to hide a gun under the coat .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Nothing seemed to come from the report ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Sumbles said .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Another former football player , Zefe Nunez , said","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"he remembers Pagourtzis as being incredibly quiet","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"and that he would n't talk to anyone .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Nunez was in the first classroom","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that Pagourtzis allegedly fired on ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and he flipped a desk","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"to shelter himself and a classmate","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"as glass shattered around him .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Nunez said","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"he ran away","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"while Pagourtzis was allegedly reloading ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that he was wearing the same black trench coat","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"he would always wear .","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"`` I heard the [ fire ]","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"alarms","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"and everybody ran out , \"","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"tenth-grader Dakota Shrader told ABC station KTRK in Houston .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"\" At first all","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"we heard","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"was ' run , run , '","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and next thing","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"you know","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"we hear , ' boom , boom , boom . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"\" Everybody started running , \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"\" and I tried to make it to the safest place","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"that I could","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"as fast","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"as I can .","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"I called my mom right away . \"","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"\" She couldn ' t breathe ,","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"she was having an asthma attack , \"","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"her mom added .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"\" I didn ' t even know where to find her . \"","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Among the injured is school district police officer John Barnes ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"who is in critical condition .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"Barnes , a retired Houston police officer , was shot in the arm","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"and suffered major bleeding ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"hospital officials said .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Two school district officers on campus were able to confront the shooter early on ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"authorities said .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"As students lined up outside the building ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"ambulances , helicopters and federal agents swarmed the school in Santa Fe , between Galveston and Houston .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"Cameras in the school are expected to provide a lot of information ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"said officials .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Kevin M. Cox /The Galveston County Daily News via AP","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"`` I ' m scared to even go back , ''","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"said one student ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"crying .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` It ' s just not something","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"that you should feel throughout the day ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"being scared .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Especially somewhere","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"where we say the Pledge of Allegiance . ''","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"\" It has been happening everywhere .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"I wasn ' t surprised","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"it happened here , \"","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"one student told KTRK .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"\" I was just scared .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"I just kept running . \"","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"This is the sixth fatal shooting at a school since the Parkland , Florida , high school shooting","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"that killed 17 students and staff in February .","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"The Parkland massacre prompted a national debate about gun reform and school safety .","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"Just last month students at Santa Fe High School participated in a nationwide school walkout against school gun violence .","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"The walkout was held on April 20","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"-- the anniversary of the 1999 Columbine High School massacre","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"that killed 13 .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"A Santa Fe student said","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"they read poems by a Parkland survivor ,","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"held 17 minutes of silence in honor of the 17 people","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"killed in Parkland ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"and discussed ways","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"they could raise gun violence awareness","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"and make their voices heard .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"School shootings have `` been going on too long in our country , ''","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"President Trump said today from the White House .","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"`` Too many years , too many decades now , we grieve for the terrible loss of life","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"and send our support and love to everyone","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"affected by this absolutely horrific attack , ''","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"Abbott said","depth":4},{"id":162,"text":"it 's time","depth":5},{"id":163,"text":"to `` make sure","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"this tragedy is never repeated ever again . ''","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"Kevin M. Cox /The Galveston County Daily News via AP","depth":4},{"id":166,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"roundtable discussions with parents , students and educators will be held .","depth":6},{"id":168,"text":"`` We want to hear from everybody","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"who has an interest in what has happened today","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"so we can work together","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"on putting together laws","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"that will protect second amendment rights","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"but at the same time ensure","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"that our communities and especially our schools are safer places , ''","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"`` My prayers are with each student , parent , educator and first responder impacted , \"","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"Education Secretary Betsy DeVos said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"\" Our schools must be safe and nurturing environments for learning .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"No student should have to experience the trauma","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"suffered by so many today and in similar events prior . \"","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"\" We simply can not allow this trend to continue , \"","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"\" Every day , the Federal Commission on School Safety is working","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"to identify proven ways","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"to prevent violence","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"and keep our students safe at school .","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"Our work remains urgent .","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"Our nation must come together","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"and address the underlying issues","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"that lead to such tragic and senseless loss of life . ''","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"Trump has ordered flags to fly at half-staff in memory of the victims .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":383,"left":346,"right":382,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":346,"left":195,"right":345,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":194,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":0,"right":193,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":345,"left":331,"right":344,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":331,"left":241,"right":330,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":198,"right":240,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":198,"left":197,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":4,"right":196,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":205,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":203,"right":204,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":201,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":200,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"